1 2024, are not subject to the renewable energy credit portfolio
2 standards or the clean energy standard.
3 (2) An energy provider described in subsection (1) whose rates
4 are regulated by the commission shall submit an amended renewable
5 energy plan as required under section 22.
6 (3) Subsection (1) does not apply after the end of the
7 Midcontinent Independent System Operator planning year ending in
8 2050.
